sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant ML

    User->>Frontend: Enter email message
    Frontend->>Frontend: Validate input (10-5000 chars)
    Frontend->>API: POST /predict {"message": "..."}
    API->>API: Validate with Pydantic
    API->>ML: Load model & vectorizer
    ML->>ML: Preprocess text
    ML->>ML: Vectorize text
    ML->>ML: Predict (spam/ham)
    ML->>ML: Calculate confidence
    ML-->>API: Return prediction
    API-->>Frontend: {"prediction": "spam", "confidence": 0.985}
    Frontend->>Frontend: Display result
    Frontend-->>User: Show classification

